profile_summary:
Arun K Nair is a highly skilled and experienced software developer with a proven track record of delivering high-quality solutions in C, JavaScript, and Python. With a strong foundation in computer science and a passion for innovation, Arun has established himself as a reliable and results-driven professional in the field of software development. 

As a seasoned developer with over 109 public repositories, Arun has demonstrated exceptional technical expertise, as well as the ability to collaborate and contribute to the open-source community. His strong online presence, with over 25 followers, is a testament to his influence and reputation as a trusted expert in his field, making him a valuable asset to any team or project.
